==Description==
The '''Damp Rock''' is a type of [[Underground|Underground Item]].

==Details==
The '''Damp Rock''' has a value of 2 [[Diamonds]] {{Diamonds}} when sold. It can also be traded in Daily Deals.

==Mine Layout==
The Damp Rock appears in the Underground as a 3x3 sized object.<br><br>
[[File:DampRockMine.png|100px]]

==Acquisition==
Damp Rocks can be found in the [[Underground]] and as Loot in [[Dungeons]].

